sourcesContent:
import React from "react";
import { FaAnchor } from "react-icons/fa";
import { IconContext } from "react-icons";
import {
  AiOutlineSetting,
  AiOutlineBulb,
  AiOutlineCloudSync,
} from "react-icons/ai";
import {
  About,
  Button,
  Description,
  Head,
  Headings,
  Logo,
  Longdescription,
  Main,
  MainGrid,
  Shortdescription,
  Subgrid1,
  Subgrid2,
  SuperSubgrid1,
} from "./Aboutus.elements";
function Aboutus() {
  return (
    <IconContext.Provider
      value={{ size: "80", stroke: "blue", strokeWidth: "1!importa" }}
    >
      <Main>
        <MainGrid>
          <Subgrid1>
            <About>About Us</About>
            <Headings>Innovating with a Digital Mindset</Headings>
            <Shortdescription>
              We are a boutique digital transformation consultancy and
              development company.
            </Shortdescription>
            <Longdescription>
              Since 2007 we have been a visionary and a reliable software
              engineering partner for world-class brands. We are a boutique
              digital transformation consultancy and software development
              company that provides cutting edge engineering solutions.
            </Longdescription>
            <Button>Get In Touch</Button>
          </Subgrid1>
          <Subgrid2>
            <SuperSubgrid1>
              <Logo>
                <FaAnchor></FaAnchor>
              </Logo>
              <Head>Experience Design</Head>
              <Description>
                In today’s digital environment, devices and consumers creating
                an expo nentially growing
              </Description>
            </SuperSubgrid1>
            <SuperSubgrid1>
              <Logo>
                <AiOutlineSetting></AiOutlineSetting>
              </Logo>
              <Head>Digital Services</Head>
              <Description>
                In today’s digital environment, devices and consumers creating
                an expo nentially growing
              </Description>
            </SuperSubgrid1>
            <SuperSubgrid1>
              <Logo>
                <AiOutlineBulb></AiOutlineBulb>
              </Logo>
              <Head>Content Engineer</Head>
              <Description>
                In today’s digital environment, devices and consumers creating
              </Description>
            </SuperSubgrid1>
            <SuperSubgrid1>
              <Logo>
                <AiOutlineCloudSync></AiOutlineCloudSync>
              </Logo>
              <Head>Data Structuring</Head>
              <Description>
                In today’s digital environment, devices and consumers creating
                an expo nentially growing
              </Description>
            </SuperSubgrid1>
          </Subgrid2>
        </MainGrid>
      </Main>
    </IconContext.Provider>
  );
}

export default Aboutus;
